{"id":595002,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/09/第四维时空-刘强东案：法治社会分分钟教你怎么/","date":"2018-09-06T06:33:00Z","modified":"2018-09-06T06:33:00Z","title":"第四维时空 | 刘强东案：法治社会分分钟教你怎么做人！","content":"<p>作者：挪威小林</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595003\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案1.jpg 660w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案1-300x169.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>01</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n今天，中国的社交网络很热闹，因为美国明尼苏达州的警察上班了，<strong>于是有关刘强东在美国涉嫌性侵害明尼苏达大学女学生案更多的资料被放了出来。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595004\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"854\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2-193x300.jpg 193w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2-768x1192.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案2-660x1024.jpg 660w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_595005\" style=\"width: 560px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-595005\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案3-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">刘强东戴上手铐被美国警方从寓所带走（图片来自网络）</span></p></div>\n<p>美国警方披露的资料显示：</p>\n<p>1.涉案人：刘强东，年龄45岁；</p>\n<p>2.涉案罪名：犯罪性行为—强奸—既遂；</p>\n<p>3.警察接警后，马上赶到现场，当场逮捕，并用随身执法记录仪记录了抓捕的全过程；</p>\n<p>4.刘强东面临的是东堤性犯罪五级中的一级指控（最高级别）CSCR-1，Criminal Sexual Conduct Rape，如罪名成立，最少判监12年，最高30年；</p>\n<p>5.控罪法条 F609.324S（<strong>C</strong>)——中的<strong>C，是指受害人有理由感到恐惧以及害怕各种情况的发生；</strong></p>\n<h3>02</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n此前中国互联网已经因为网络上的一张图片纷纷猜测，京东创始人可能牵涉入一宗性侵案。</p>\n<p>但没有进一步资料，以及不熟悉美国的法律，认为刘强东牵涉的可能只是轻罪，酒后猥亵或性骚扰，<strong>因为他很快便能从监狱无保释出来，并以光的速度返回祖国大陆。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595006\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"231\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案4.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案4-300x138.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>新浪微博实名认证的蓝V“京东发言人，在9月2日发表声明：</p>\n<blockquote><p>今日，我们关注到了微博上有一些用户在散布关于刘强东先生的一些<strong>不实传言</strong>。特此声明如下：</p>\n<p>刘强东先生在美国商务活动期间，遭遇到了失实的指控，经过当地警方调查，<strong>未发现有任何不当行为</strong>，他将按照原计划继续其形成。我们针对不实报道或造谣行为采取必要的法律行动。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595007\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"669\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5-224x300.jpg 224w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5-768x1027.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案5-766x1024.jpg 766w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>刘强东火速回国后，马上就现身京东总部出席与如意集团的签约仪式。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595008\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案6.jpg 766w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案6-300x239.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>03</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n京东一方面出动律师信恐吓各位网民，不要信谣传谣，否则会付出严重的代价，另一方面，水军也没闲着，事件一出，由“末那大叔”带头的营销公众号开始转发一篇“洗地稿：《<strong>刘强东事件：世道变坏，都是从小人狂欢开始的》</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595009\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1586\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7-95x300.jpg 95w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7-768x2435.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案7-323x1024.jpg 323w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595010\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"738\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8-203x300.jpg 203w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8-768x1134.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案8-694x1024.jpg 694w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595011\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"722\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9-208x300.jpg 208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9-768x1110.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案9-709x1024.jpg 709w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595012\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"720\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10-208x300.jpg 208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10-768x1106.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案10-711x1024.jpg 711w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>微博也没闲着，营销号到处刷一篇短文：“刘强东先生是中国人，全球华人都应该站在该站的立场”、“希望所有华人都不要当卖国贼，被外来别有用心的势力、声音所利用”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595013\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"721\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11-208x300.jpg 208w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11-768x1108.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案11-710x1024.jpg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595014\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"689\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12-218x300.jpg 218w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12-768x1058.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案12-743x1024.jpg 743w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>04</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n幸而案件是在美国发生的，没有“我大清自有国情在此”，无论请多少水军都挡不住美国的司法正义。</p>\n<p>刘强东此前之所以能从监狱无保释出来，并可行动自如地回国，根据微博认证为@SLPD圣利安住市警察局 蓝V的解释：</p>\n<p>1.警察是掌握了一定合理的依据才实施逮捕的，并且可以不经法院签发逮捕令而当场实施逮捕；</p>\n<p>2.9月3日，是美国的“劳动节”，检察院不上班，刘强东是8月31日深夜被捕的，因此能见到检察官肯定是72小时后，而72小时内美元检方起诉，警方就必须放人；</p>\n<p>3.进入公诉阶段，法官会决定被告在候审期间是否需要被关押，如果法官认为不需要关押，则会根据被告人的前科记录和再犯风险等因素，决定他的保释额度。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595015\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1723\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13.jpg 1000w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13-87x300.jpg 87w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13-768x2646.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案13-297x1024.jpg 297w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>05</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n也就是说，刘强东能够顺利从警察局出来，并回国，是因为美国当地在放“劳动节”假期，检察院在放假，警方无权羁押他太久，所以让他无保释出来了，<strong>而非@京东公关 所说的“经过当地警方调查，未发现有任何不当行为。”</strong></p>\n<p>果然，明尼苏达州的警察局在9月4日一上班，马上就在网上公布了更多的涉案资料，坐实了刘强东涉嫌的不是早前网上猜测的是最轻一级的“五级轻罪”，而是“侵入式性行为”的一级重罪。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案14.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595016\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案14.jpg 639w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案14-300x194.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案14-230x150.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>06</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n明尼苏达州警察公告更多刘强东涉案的资料后，京东的股价应声大跌5.97%，市值蒸发157亿人民币。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595017\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"890\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15-768x1366.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案15-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595018\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"653\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16-230x300.jpg 230w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16-768x1003.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案16-784x1024.jpg 784w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这还不是终结，只是刚刚开始，京东是美国纳斯达克的上市公司，上市公司要向公众如实披露公司高管的信息，<strong>针对@京东公关 此前所发的声明，美国有三间法律公司分别宣布要调查京东是否失实披露刘强东的案情。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595019\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17-267x300.jpg 267w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17-768x864.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案17-910x1024.jpg 910w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595020\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"563\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18-266x300.jpg 266w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18-768x865.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案18-909x1024.jpg 909w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595021\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"703\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19-213x300.jpg 213w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19-768x1080.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案19-728x1024.jpg 728w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<h3>07</h3>\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\n所谓，恐吓网友一时爽，遇着美帝就分分钟教你重新做人。</p>\n<p>一宗在美帝发生的华人案件，是中国社会一堂生动的司法课程，我们与文明还有很大的差距。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595022\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"683\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20.jpg 1079w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20-220x300.jpg 220w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20-768x1049.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案20-750x1024.jpg 750w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595023\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"750\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21-200x300.jpg 200w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/刘强东案21-683x1024.jpg 683w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/第四维时空.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-595025\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/第四维时空.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"224\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/第四维时空.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/09/第四维时空-300x168.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,9203],"tags":[33760,16773,15901,34255,9019,19607]}